{"tid":1080124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠做「媒人」不成 林鄭拒與中聯辦王志民握手","createTime":"2019-03-27T11:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T21:14:30.000Z","uid":29627,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b7886c2fda5514ca49dec8fa1048dfb2f18d89","tid":1080124,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"【世紀一幕】李嘉誠做「媒人」不成 林鄭拒與中聯辦王志民握手 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190327/large/1553682853_02f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190327%2Flarge%2F1553682853_02f3.jpg&h=bb80457e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭拒與王志民握手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190327/large/1553682859_12b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190327%2Flarge%2F1553682859_12b7.jpg&h=99f7a36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭沒有理會扶她下車的李嘉誠，將其甩在身後。<br />\n<br />\n政治人物握手禮儀向來甚多盤算，「拒握手」常引起討論，今日又有特首林鄭月娥，拒絕與中聯辦主任王志民握手，未知林鄭心底打甚麼盤算？ <br />\n<br />\n慈山寺今舉行開光典禮，猛人雲集，除邀得長實資深顧問李嘉誠三父子外，林鄭月娥及中聯辦主任王志民亦為嘉賓。活動至揭幕儀式臨完結時，李嘉誠上前與林鄭熱情握手，短說幾句話後，李轉身向站在另一邊的王志民，用左手拉著王志民的手，並向林鄭伸出右手，疑為「撮合」二人握手，電光火石間林鄭轉身面向觀眾方向，拒絕了誠哥一番美意，而王志民反應亦快，已伸出去的手隨即收回。<br />\n<br />\n而於典禮較早時間，林鄭與李嘉誠同車前住揭幕場地，兩人同時下車，期間後排的李嘉誠伸手向前，扶林鄭下車，不過林鄭並沒有回頭，而是一直向會場前進，將年老的李嘉誠甩在身後。<br />\n<br />\n反觀李嘉誠今日活動間，與中聯辦主任王志民狀甚親暱，常互相握住對方的手。<br />\n<br />\n大埔洞梓慈山寺由李嘉誠豪擲逾17億元興建，於2014年落成，今年再完成擴建。其中2萬多呎的佛教藝術博物館，5月1日起免費開放予公眾預約參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190327/59419174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59419174&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl4m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=a8bdf4fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59419174&h=0f7c34da\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190327/59419174</a>"},{"pid":"a72446549f658a0094fd2f429174b83e5a890fb2","tid":1080124,"uid":180156,"like":34,"dislike":13,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"一時睇唔到<br />\n就俾人作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0908d4830ddb00867663cdb6de2c4120702ee922","tid":1080124,"uid":28195,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭心諗：床都上埋喇，仲握咩手呀，你會唔會同老公老婆，無喇喇握手呢？"},{"pid":"b97b778c57ca11ed02e894aaa7fff696ddb7952c","tid":1080124,"uid":130695,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"0908d4830ddb00867663cdb6de2c4120702ee922","tid":1080124,"uid":28195,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭心諗：床都上埋喇，仲握咩手呀，你會唔會同老公老婆，無喇喇握手呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"晚晚渣棍啦 仲渣排"},{"pid":"4c8193f5a216cece6ee0560e969624e48c84a89e","tid":1080124,"uid":52459,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"疆果然越老越辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d391d2616402bb581534b801a4427db903a6ee85","tid":1080124,"uid":103156,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"癩蛤蟆想吃月鵝肉！老幾呀你。"},{"pid":"5182961e285c0c0e972c8dd5b57071c29ea0bfa1","tid":1080124,"uid":20522,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"d391d2616402bb581534b801a4427db903a6ee85","tid":1080124,"uid":103156,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"癩蛤蟆想吃月鵝肉！老幾呀你。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n淋病係近平架"},{"pid":"dfe68d98f3148bc5ca53b02da277bd153e26425d","tid":1080124,"uid":63311,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:3